divs: sighting detailssighting report: to whom it may concern, on saturday, 3\26\05 late afternoon i was engrossed in taking shots of the prism i noticed in the sky. there was lots of plane pollution that day (some call them chemtrails. whatever they are -they are an aggrevation to me as a photographer as it ruins good color shots.) i proceeded to snap at the sky on the ride home from a local park. i never looked at the photos i took that day till the next day, sunday.i also did not notice the anomoly\ufo\whatever it is when i took the photos as my mind was more focused on the prism. in looking over the shots i have 2 photos with the most unusual anomoly. i don t believe it is a "sunspot" nor anything reflecting from within the vehicle as my window was wide open. i d be happy to share these with whomever altho i found nothing in the sight that tells me how to share digital photos. from what i can tell, i must send the negatives. i have no "negatives". i have the originals in my computer. any suggestions would be greatly appreciated. our scientific minds are stumped on this one!! date taken: 3\26\05 time taken: between 5:13 pm and 5:22pm. the 2 photos that show that weird thing were taken at exactly 5:21;19 pm and 5:21:20. one second apart. there is a big change in the "anomoly" in one second. i have a series of shots of the prism that i believe was caused by the overhead air traffic.where the sun was setting there was alot of pollution. sincerely, kim picard
